[US trip self-maintenance cheat sheet, Windows and i.MX8, 2026-5]

1. ipLocator
This is suppposed to be executed in Windows to obtain the DHCP IP address of i.MX8 once i.MX8 boots up.
Double click ipLocator.bat and get the following results.  In the following scenario, Windows bears the DHCP IP address 172.16.14.28.  i.MX8 bears the DHCP IP address 172.16.14.61.

